    <requirements>ID_GMBINDER_WOW5E_CLASS_DRUID</requirements>
    <description>
      <p>While shapeshifted, you can spend 1 affinity point and use your action to let out an enchanted roar. Each ally within 60 feet of you that can hear you have their movement speed increased by 10 feet until the end of their next turn, including you.</p>
    </description>
